  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 10cd6cfa10c047e48accda1f214da0b5, type: 2}
  replyText:
  - Give me a role where I overexplain or monologue, and I'll be golden.
  - Just don't ask me to express a lot of emotion.
  - Well, I'm hoping for something pretty laid-back, you know. Like cool uncle or
    something.
  - Ooh, make me like a performer or a vocalist!
  - Oh, just give the role of an asshole or something.
  - Give me an expressive role. I shall moan, groan and wail.
  - Any role is fine. I'll try my best in becoming them.
  - Make me like an underdog. I can take physical abuse. And verbal.
  - I should be the protagonist, with dead parents and dark mind...
  - Maybe a hostage, I'm fine with being tied up... but uh, I'm fine with most things.
  - I'm fine with most things! I don't even need scripts most of the time! I just
    make it up on the fly.
  - As long as I can keep my natural smell combined with Axe pray deoderant.
  - Oh, please please PLEASE let me be in a romantic story. I'll for sure find my
    soulmate there!
  - Maybe a person who knows more than those around him. The smart or survivalist
    guy, I guess.
  - Oh, that's easy. Put me in the role of a sensitive, emotional person.
  - Give me the role of an extroverted person, like a talkative friend or a leader!
  - well, just don't put me in any role where i gotta be happy or something. i can't
    fake that.
  - Well, one thing's for sure. Don't make an acrobat! Or anything physically intensive.
  - Uh, honestly... I'm not sure. Maybe something not too mentally taxing?
  - Whatever it is, don't give me a block of words. I ain't remembering allat.
  - I'm good with whatever, just make sure I'm allowed to laugh. Trust me, I can
    laugh at ANYTHING.
  - Welllll, I should be good with anything... but maybe not as wel... hmmmm...
  - Maybe like a hard-boiled police lieutenant. Just someone where I'm allowed to
    be pissed off and shout.
